public abstract java.lang.String getCapitalizedName()

getUppercaseLetter

public abstract java.lang.String getUppercaseLetter()
Return uppercase letter identifying the color. Returns "B", "W", or "E". This letter is not internationalized, such that it can be used for instance in standard language independent game results (e.g. "W+3").
